#

Saffron Risotto with Grilled Shrimp

40 min
$15
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

shellfishdairy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freeseafood

Cuisine:

ItalianMediterranean

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

easyquickgourmetcomfort food

Description

A creamy, flavorful risotto infused with saffron and topped with succulent grilled shrimp for a gourmet touch.

Ingredients

  • arborio rice: 1 cup
  • chicken or vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • saffron threads: 1 pinch
  • white wine: 1/2 cup
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • shrimp: 1 pound, peeled and deveined
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley: for garnish
